description: The mixed use redevelopment of the eastern part of the former Hither Green Hospital Site, Hither Green Lane SE13 comprising a total of 493 residential units, a leisure/health club, 13 live/work units, retail (Class A1) and office/caf (Classes B1/A3) space including the retention of the group of buildings to the north east corner of the site at the junction of Hither Green Lane and George Lane to provide a doctor's surgery, crche and 3 live/work units, together with the provision of new vehicular accesses to Hither Green Lane and Woodlands Street, associated parking and landscaping, the formation of a public piazza and retention of the water tower as a site management office.
